            "answer": "<p>1. Open the charging case, then press and hold the button. Wait for a blue light to pulse.<br>2. Select your headphones from your device's Bluetooth list.<br>3. On your device, download the Bluetooth app, and follow the in-app instructions to complete the set-up.</p>"
