          "settings": {
            "question": "What is active noise cancelling?",
            "answer": "<p>Active Noise Cancellation is the technology that drowns out unwanted sounds when you are listening to your music. These headphones utilise four microphones to constantly measure the surrounding noise and automatically adjust the level of noise cancellation you need to focus.</p>"
